209
00:09:32,102 --> 00:09:36,043
So, as you grow older, your eyes change quite a lot.

210
00:09:36,043 --> 00:09:39,065
As many people know, you're likely to get more long-sighted,

211
00:09:39,065 --> 00:09:40,245
likely to need glasses,

212
00:09:40,245 --> 00:09:44,367
